Exception Hierarchy :
	1. Exception
	2. Error
	
	
	Finally block will always get executed : True
	If JVM will not get terminated 
	
	try     : To maintain the Risky Code 
	Catch   : To handle the Risky Code 
	finally : To maintain the Cleanup code 
	throw   : To hand over the created exception object to the JVM Manually.
	throws  : to delegate the Responsibility  
	
	
